July 28, 2017 11:38 PM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a stock life insurance company in the United States. The company offers qualified and nonqualified annuity contracts that include various funding and payout options for individuals and employer-sponsored retirement plans, as well as nonqualified deferred compensation plans and related services. Its products and services include deferred and immediate annuity contracts; programs offered to qualified plans and nonqualified deferred compensation plans that package administrative and record-keeping services, participant education, and retirement readiness planning tools along with various investment option...
Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a stock life insurance company in the United States. The company offers qualified and nonqualified annuity contracts that include various funding and payout options for individuals and employer-sponsored retirement plans, as well as nonqualified deferred compensation plans and related services. Its products and services include deferred and immediate annuity contracts; programs offered to qualified plans and nonqualified deferred compensation plans that package administrative and record-keeping services, participant education, and retirement readiness planning tools along with various investment options comprising proprietary and non-proprietary mutual funds, and variable and fixed investment options; wrapper agreements entered into with retirement plans, which contain certain benefit responsive guarantees; and value products and pension risk transfer solutions to institutional plan sponsors. The company provides its products to individuals, pension plans, and small to mid-sized corporations, as well as to employer-sponsored groups in the health care, government, and education markets. It distributes its products through pension professionals, independent agents and brokers, third party administrators, banks, consultants, and career agents, as well as planning and advisory representatives and financial guidance planners. The company was formerly known as ING Life Insurance and Annuity Company and changed its name to Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company in September 2014. Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company is based in Windsor, Connecticut. Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company is a subsidiary of Voya Holdings Inc.
Detailed Description


