					Will You Have EnoughOrange Money™ for Retirement?				




Tool
			






 





Earn more on your money with a guaranteed, competitive, fixed interest rate, while you defer paying taxes until you take a withdrawal. 




Key Features

Competitive guaranteed interest rate1
Tax-deferred growth – you don’t pay income tax unless you take a withdrawal2
No contribution limits on a deferred annuity
Can turn your contract into a series of income payments                      
 

Products






 


					Voya Guarantee Choice Annuity 




Product
                        





A tax-deferred annuity that credits your premium with a guaranteed competitive interest rate for a retirement income stream you can count on. 







 


					Voya Select Rate Annuity 




Product
                        





Grow your retirement savings in a predictable way that is guaranteed and tax deferred with Voya Select Rate Annuity.







 


					Voya Lifetime Income Annuity 




Product
                        





Voya Lifetime Income helps you turn a portion of your savings into supplemental retirement income, with guaranteed increases to that income the longer you wait to start. 





Related Items







 


					Is an Annuity Right for You?  




Article
			
















Voya Guarantee Choice Annuity is issued by Voya Insurance and Annuity Company (Des Moines, IA), member of the Voya ™ family of companies.  Contract Form Series:  IU-IA-3036, may vary by state and may not be available in all states.
Voya Select Rate Annuity is issued by Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company (Windsor, CT) and distributed by Directed Services LLC. Both companies are members of the Voya ™ family of companies. 





1All guarantees are based on the financial strength and claims paying ability of Voya Insurance and Annuity Company and Voya Retirement Insurance and Annuity Company, who are solely responsible for all obligations under its polices
2Withdrawals may be subject to Federal/State income tax and, if taken prior to age 59½, an additional 10% Federal penalty tax. IRAs and other qualified plans already provide tax-deferral like that provided by an annuity. Additional features and benefits, such as contract guarantees, death benefits and the ability to receive a lifetime income are contained within the annuity for a cost. Please be sure the features and costs of the annuity are right for you when considering the purchase of the annuity. 














 








